    <h1 class="hero-h">11 Claude prompts <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">for customer success.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Twelve production-grade Claude prompts for Customer Success professionals at B2B companies. Each one is built around a real CS job, from onboarding plans and QBR decks to health-score triage, churn saves, renewal prep, and expansion plays. Copy a prompt, swap in your account details, and run it.</p>
